6 12:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-deadly-disease-outbreak-map-flags-highly-vulnerable-regions-around-the-world</guid></item><item><title>量子信息机器学习利用实用的量子优势来预测时空混沌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-informed-machine-learning-for-predicting-spatiotemporal-chaos-with-practical-quantum-advantage</link><description>最终，QIML 证明我们不需要完全容错的量子计算机来看到结果。通过使用量子处理器来学习复杂的混沌“规则”，我们可以为经典计算机提供所需的推动力，以对自然世界中最动荡的环境做出可靠的长期预测。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-informed-machine-learning-for-predicting-spatiotemporal-chaos-with-practical-quantum-advantage2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 12:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-informed-machine-learning-for-predicting-spatiotemporal-chaos-with-practical-quantum-advantage</guid></item><item><title>TSC2 GAP 结构域 V1646Cfs*7 变体改变结节性硬化症复合体中的蛋白质稳定性和相互作用网络</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/tsc2-gap-domain-v1646cfs7-variant-alters-protein-stability-and-interaction-networks-in-tuberous-sclerosis-complex</link><description>该网站使用安全服务来防范恶意机器人。当网站验证您不是机器人时会显示此页面。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tsc2-gap-domain-v1646cfs7-variant-alters-protein-stability-and-interaction-networks-in-tuberous-sclerosis-complex.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 12:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/tsc2-gap-domain-v1646cfs7-variant-alters-protein-stability-and-interaction-networks-in-tuberous-sclerosis-complex</guid></item><item><title>氧化应激导致老年脊椎动物大脑中去泛素化酶活性可逆性降低</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/oxidative-stress-causes-a-reversible-decrease-of-deubiquitylases-activity-in-old-vertebrate-brains</link><description>基于活性的蛋白质组学揭示了氧化应激驱动的衰老脊椎动物大脑中去泛素化酶活性的保守性下降。抗氧化治疗可恢复活性，将氧化还原敏感的 DUB 识别为蛋白质稳态下降的早期驱动因素。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/oxidative-stress-causes-a-reversible-decrease-of-